block SignupModal 
    #signup.cd-popup(role='alert')
        .cd-popup-container
            .col-sm-12.col-sm-offset-1(style='background-color:white')
                form#signup-contact-form.contact-form(action='/users',method='POST')
                    .form-group
                    br
                    br
                    a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block(href='/auth/facebook')
                      i.fa.fa-facebook.fa-lg
                      | &nbsp; &nbsp;Signup with Facebook
                    hr
                    .form-group
                    label.input_label Name
                    input(
                        type='text', id='name', name='name', class='form-control', 
                        placeholder='Your Name', required, autofocus
                    )
                    .form-group
                    label.input_label Email address
                    input(
                        type='email', id='email', name='email', class='form-control', 
                        placeholder='Email address', required, autofocus
                    )
                    .form-group
                    label.input_label Password 
                    input(
                    type='password', id='password', name='password', class='form-control', 
                    placeholder='Password', required, autofocus
                    )
                    .form-group
                    label.input_label Confirm Password 
                    input(
                    type='password', id='password_confirmation', name='password_confirmation', class='form-control', 
                    placeholder='Confirm Password', required, autofocus
                    )
                    hr
                    .form-group
                      | 회원 가입하면 루나비앤비의 서비스 약관, 비차별 정책, 결제 서비스 약관, 개인정보 보호정책, 
